;; Genre base: モダンリメイク (Modern Remake)
{:genre/id :modern-remake
 :genre/status :not-applicable
 :genre/note
 "This is a production/marketing category (remaking an existing older game
  with modern tech) -- it describes a RELATIONSHIP between two versions of
  a product, not a gameplay mechanic. There is no distinct core loop to
  author here; a \"remake\" of any of the other 17 bases in this repo would
  just be a second, differently-tuned copy of that base, not a new
  archetype. No games/ dir -- nothing honest to build."}
